&lt;h1 id="why-you-need-to-be-in-silicon-valley"&gt;Why You Need to be in Silicon Valley&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 17 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For years I didn&amp;rsquo;t believe this. I thought that you could take advantage of the benefits of Boston, Seattle, NY, Austin – cheaper talent, no echo chamber, local Universities, etc.. But I give up. I found myself telling an entrepreneur why he had to be in Silicon Valley if he wanted to succeed. Most of my points are about Consumer Internet businesses&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Unquantifiable Risk</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/unquantifiable-risk/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Nov 2005 12:54:17 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/unquantifiable-risk/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/unquantifiable-risk.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
